1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,639
Deep inside the temple, a mysterious note triggers something no one expected.

2
00:00:06,639 --> 00:00:19,315
The adventurer and Mu Young are SUDDENLY transported into Tristan's Tomb — and there, materializing from swirling purple smoke... is a Junior Balrog.

3
00:00:19,315 --> 00:00:20,436
Wings spread.

4
00:00:20,436 --> 00:00:21,557
Eyes burning.

5
00:00:21,557 --> 00:00:25,438
The seal on the floor is cracked and glowing.

6
00:00:25,438 --> 00:00:32,681
This is not the full Balrog — not yet — but it is proof... that the prison is leaking.

7
00:00:32,681 --> 00:00:36,906
The dead hero's tomb... has become the battlefield.
